  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12 more-features section-description wow fadeIn animated">
        <h2>TRYING TO MANAGE YOUR BILLS AND BUDGET?</h2>
        <div class="divider-1 wow fadeInUp animated"><span></span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-5 more-features-box wow fadeInLeft animated">
        <%= image_tag('landing/pc.png', alt: '') %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-7 more-features-box wow fadeInUp animated" >
        <div class="more-features-box-text">
          <div class="more-features-box-text-icon">
            <span aria-hidden="true" class="typcn typcn-attachment"></span>
          </div>
          <h3>MANAGE EVERYTHING IN ONE PLACE</h3>
          <div class="more-features-box-text-description">
            See all your accounts,  investments, expenses and incomes in one place.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="more-features-box-text">
          <div class="more-features-box-text-icon">
            <span aria-hidden="true" class="typcn typcn-user"></span>
          </div>
          <h3>KNOW WHERE YOUR MONEY GOES</h3>
          <div class="more-features-box-text-description">
            Gaining control of your financial situation and using money to help you reach your goals is possible.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="more-features-box-text">
          <div class="more-features-box-text-icon">
            <span aria-hidden="true" class="typcn typcn-user"></span>
          </div>
          <h3>STICK TO A BUDGET</h3>
          <div class="more-features-box-text-description">
            Create budgets and make a plan for wise spending. Know how much you can spend while sticking to your budget..
          </div>
        </div>        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
